				\begin{document} $$ log(\beta_{t}) = log(\beta_{0}) - \alpha_{D} \frac{\Delta D_{t}}{N}  $$ \end{document}log(βt)=log(β0)−αDΔDtN

where \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
